<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<node name="vcfFilterJs"
	label="VCF Filter JS" 
	xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
	>

  <description>
     <h3>Motivation</h3>
     <p>See  <a href="https://github.com/lindenb/jvarkit/wiki/VCFFilterJS">https://github.com/lindenb/jvarkit/wiki/VCFFilterJS</a>.Filters a VCF with javascript ( java rhino engine http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhino_%28JavaScript_engine%29 ).  the script binds the following variables:</p>
     
    <ul>
	    <li>variant : the current variation; a org.broadinstitute.variant.variantcontext.VariantContext ( https://samtools.github.io/htsjdk/javadoc/htsjdk/htsjdk/variant/variantcontext/VariantContext.html )</li>
		<li>header : the VCF header org.broadinstitute.variant.vcf.VCFHeader ( https://samtools.github.io/htsjdk/javadoc/htsjdk/htsjdk/variant/vcf/VCFHeader.html ).</li>
		<li>snpEff a java.util.List of SnpEffPredictionParser$SnpEffPrediction ( https://github.com/lindenb/jvarkit/blob/master/src/main/java/com/github/lindenb/jvarkit/util/vcf/predictions/SnpEffPredictionParser.java )</li>
		<li>vep a java.util.List of VepPredictionParser$VepPrediction ( https://github.com/lindenb/jvarkit/blob/master/src/main/java/com/github/lindenb/jvarkit/util/vcf/predictions/VepPredictionParser.java ) .</li>
	</ul>
	<p>the script should return '1' or true if the current VCF file should be printed.</p>
     
     <xi:include href="footer.html" xpointer="xpointer(/div/*)" parse="xml" />
  </description>


   <xi:include href="inport.vcf.xml"/>
   <xi:include href="outport.vcf_count.xml"/>

 <property type="column" name="vcfInput" label="VCF path" description="VCF files" data-type="string"  port="input"/>
  <property type="string" name="javascript" label="javascript code" default="false;" multiline="true"/>
 
  <description>
     <xi:include href="footer.html" xpointer="xpointer(/div/*)" parse="xml" />
  </description>
  
  <xi:include href="code.vcffilterjs.xml" parse="xml" />

 <view class="com.github.lindenb.knime5bio.bio.VcfNodeView"/>  
</node>

